ent as a sentry, watching, waiting, expecting SOMETHING in his heart of hearts......but unsure of what exactly. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bfaeryfirealongthenightshore.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nyar999>nyar999</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.coneyislandwhitefish.com/fly.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Deus Ex Machina / Causa Sui</span><br>  Posts: 53<br> <font color=#333333>(2/27/03 5:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/ffaeryfirealongthenightshorefrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=65>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: trapped in transition</span><hr size=1> <br>
